# Regenerable / transient — Drive-backed (reports are also auto-published to Drive). The one
# exception: the studio-authored targets Word (the only .docx under outputs/) is NOT
# regenerable, so it is tracked in git too — Drive + GitHub both back it up.
outputs/**
!outputs/**/
!outputs/**/*.docx
verification_report.md
_test/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
smbpub_*

